name: Fix Selected Code
description: Fix bugs, type errors, or logical issues in selected code
---
The user has selected code that contains a bug, type error, or logical issue. Fix it with minimal changes.

1. Identify the root cause
2. Provide the corrected code
3. Explain the fix briefly (one sentence if possible)
4. If the fix requires changes to other files, mention them explicitly

Preserve existing formatting, naming conventions, and style. Do not refactor beyond what is necessary to fix the issue.
